INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================

Follow these steps in the exact order shown to deploy tool:

1) become the root user
2) run the install_from_repo.sh script from GIT to fetch auto_deploy from GIT repo.
3) run auto_deploy setup-config, this will create a sample config file in the /etc/mariadb location.
4) tweak configuration file to desired config as per customer's request, see comments in the file for help.

To read documentation for the tool run auto_deploy --help.

